---
const projects = [
  {
    title: "DON",
    subtitle: "Personal AI Infrastructure",
    bullets: [
      "Persönliches AI-Betriebssystem",
      "Skill-basierter Assistent mit Memory und strukturiertem Problemlösen",
      "33 spezialisierte Fähigkeiten"
    ],
    tags: ["Claude Code", "Obsidian"],
    status: "Aktiv"
  },
  {
    title: "Context Map",
    bullets: [
      "Komplettes Kontextinventar über alle AI-Systeme und Wissensquellen",
      "Token-bewusstes Laden",
      "Progressive Disclosure für Kontext"
    ],
    tags: ["Knowledge Management", "Token Optimization"],
    status: "Aktiv"
  }
]
---

<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="DON AI Systems - Persönliche AI-Infrastruktur. Systeme, die mitdenken." />
    <title>DON AI Systems</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Cormorant:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=supreme@400,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="bio">
          <img src="/don-logo.png" alt="DON" class="logo" />
          <h1>DON AI<br/>Systems</h1>
          <p class="tagline">Systeme, die mitdenken.</p>

          <div class="about">
            <p>Ich baue persönliche AI-Infrastruktur. Nicht Tools, die man benutzt, sondern Systeme, die einen kennen. Die wissen, was wichtig ist, was als nächstes kommt und wo das Wissen liegt.</p>
            <p>Das Ziel: AI, die nicht bei null anfängt. Sondern da weitermacht, wo man aufgehört hat.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="details">
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="label">Stack</span>
              <span>Claude Code, Obsidian, TypeScript</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <span class="label">Fokus</span>
              <span>AI Infrastructure, Knowledge Systems</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="links">
            <a href="mailto:info@donsystems.de">info@donsystems.de</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/DON-AI-Systems" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="content">
        <section class="projects">
          <h2>Projekte</h2>
          {projects.map((project) => (
            <article class="project">
              <div class="project-header">
                <h3>{project.title}</h3>
                <span class="status">{project.status}</span>
              </div>
              {project.subtitle && <p class="project-subtitle">{project.subtitle}</p>}
              <ul class="project-bullets">
                {project.bullets.map((bullet) => (
                  <li>{bullet}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
              <div class="tags">
                {project.tags.map((tag) => (
                  <span class="tag">{tag}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </section>

      </main>
    </div>

    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      :root {
        --bg: #f0ebe3;
        --text: #2c2c2c;
        --text-light: #6b6b6b;
        --accent: #8b7355;
        --border: #d4cdc4;
        --tag-bg: #e6e0d6;
        --font-headline: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
        --font-body: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
        --font-body-alt: 'Supreme', 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
        --font-ui: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
        --font-caps: 'Barlow Condensed', 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
      }

      html {
        font-size: 16px;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .container {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100vh;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
      }

      .sidebar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        width: 400px;
        min-width: 400px;
        height: 100vh;
        padding: 4rem 3rem 4rem 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .bio {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: var(--font-headline);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        color: var(--text);
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-family: var(--font-body-alt);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: var(--text-light);
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .about p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .about p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .details {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding-top: 0.5rem;
      }

      .detail-item {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.1rem;
        font-family: var(--font-ui);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      .label {
        font-family: var(--font-caps);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 0.5rem;
      }

      .links a {
        font-family: var(--font-ui);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-bottom: 2px;
        transition: border-color 0.2s;
      }

      .links a:hover {
        border-color: var(--text);
      }

      .content {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 4rem 0 4rem 3rem;
        border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-caps);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .projects {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }

      .project {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .project:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .project-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      }

      .project h3 {
        font-family: var(--font-headline);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .status {
        font-family: var(--font-ui);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-light);
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .project-subtitle {
        font-family: var(--font-caps);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      }

      .project-bullets {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }

      .project-bullets li {
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      }

      .tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.4rem;
      }

      .tag {
        font-family: var(--font-ui);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        color: var(--text-light);
        background: var(--tag-bg);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          flex-direction: column;
          padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }

        .sidebar {
          position: relative;
          width: 100%;
          min-width: unset;
          height: auto;
          padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
          border-left: none;
          border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .logo {
          width: 48px;
          height: 48px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
